item.description:
Session variables are easy to use in meteor. the can ve get and set from the javascript code using:
Session.get('variableName'); Session.set('variableName', true);  on your HTML you can reference the get method easily by:
&lt;template name=&quot;admin&quot;&gt; {{#if $.Session.get 'variableName'}} I am here {{else}} I am not here {{/if}} &lt;/template&gt;
